author: desruisseaux
msg: Merged ReferencingIdentifier with Identifier. This reflect a change in ISO standards,
where MD_Identifier and RS_Identifier (from ISO 19115:2003) have been merged in the
MD_Identifier type in ISO 19115:2014. Concequently all usages of ServiceIdentifier in
Apache SIS have been replaced by usage of the Identifier parent type.
